snippet.title: James Franco Reveals He Would Get Signed To Marvel If He Told The Truth...
snippet.description:
In the court case that continues to rage on between Johnny and Amber Heard, it's becoming more and more about who can prove what instead of who is saying what in regards to what happened in their brief marriage turned bitter divorce. We say that because in the early parts of 2022, the main court case, in this case the massive Defamation suit that Depp has against Heard, is going to FINALLY be taken to court. So whatever proof, big or small, that can be found or proven is going to be vital, and apparently that also applies to the testimonies of some key people. We'll break it down for you, be sure to like the video and subscribe to the channel!

Click HERE To Enter The GIVEAWAY! 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC76r9K-_Knc7d38c9uKRwaw?sub_confirmation=1 

And there you have it, everyone! A look at the situation with Johnny Depp and Amber Heard and how James Franco, as well as Elon Musk, might just be the key witnesses to try and change what is going on and being perceived in the trial. Do you think their words might help Johnny Depp? Do they honestly know things that they haven't revealed to anyone before? Let us know in the comments below, be sure to subscribe and we'll see you next time on the channel!
